  <p class="gd-lede">Alaska is the world's most extreme heliski destination — a place of steep spines, deep maritime snow and huge vertical in the Chugach. This guide covers where to go, the season, cost and who it suits, and offers an honest look at our <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a> <a href="/packages">packages</a> as an alternative.</p>
